&lt;?char 13?&gt;
In a perfect world, you'd take the time to fully understand the principle of least privilege. Read Andreas Wolter's post on who should be the database owner, and check out Denny Cherry's book Securing SQL Server for more details.&lt;?char 13?&gt;
&lt;?char 13?&gt;
